Durable and functional coatings. PFAS-free nano technology.
Durable polysilazane ceramic coating. Curing time from days to seconds.
Low temperature curing below 100°C. Replacement for PFAS.
World-leading low coefficient of friction.
Problems we solve: create rapidly cured, hard, functional polysilazane coatings;
provide PFAS-free alternatives to impending PFAS bans;
match specific performance requirements across industries.
What makes us special: PFAS-free coatings more slippery than Teflon®;
ultra-rapid hard cure < 30 seconds below 100°C without catalyst; excellent hydrophobicity;
validated by FTIR across 10,000+ samples on stainless steel, aluminium, glass, TPU.
Functional additives covalently bond to polymer backbone.
Applicable by slot-die, ultrasonic spray, other wet chemistry in roll-to-roll or sheet processes.
Patent-pending compositions and processes. Environmental responsibility.
Market fits: windows/building easy-to-clean; touchscreens/displays/optics; electronics encapsulation;
cookware; blades/cutters/slitters; plastic films; solar/wind; car wrapping.

